{"tid":1607330,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「蜜大腿」創始人竟然不是U-IE，而是「蜜腿時代」的她！","createTime":"2019-09-30T19:55:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T00:43:31.000Z","uid":34643,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e507dbf4561af8f1652f722849b1d6aafa6d9723","tid":1607330,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:55:53.000Z","msg":"說起「蜜大腿」，大家的腦海裡是不是最先想到的是U-IE。<br />\n<br />\n所謂「蜜大腿」就是形容雙腿猶如蜂蜜一樣，充滿光澤與彈性；同時腿部的曲線圓潤流暢、緊實勻稱有質感。 比起以往大部分女性憧憬的小細腿，「蜜大腿」更能散發令人心動的性感氣質。<br />\n<br />\nU-IE還是After School時期的時候，「蜜大腿」就成了她的最佳代名詞，甚至因為她「蜜大腿」這個詞才火速躥紅，被廣大網民和粉絲所知道。 雙腿圓潤線條流暢，完全不是骨感美，而是性感的線條美。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-09-30/120586-775569.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-09-30%2F120586-775569.jpeg&h=2f09fb55&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_ff39240c7e9d2c5a87a671f4138ec76a/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-09-30/120586-775574.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_ff39240c7e9d2c5a87a671f4138ec76a%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-09-30%2F120586-775574.jpeg&h=1054c890&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但其實，還有一個人比在U-IE擁有蜜大腿稱號之前，已經是蜜腿代表了，她就是IU。 別看現在的IU瘦弱嬌小，2009年《BOO》時期還帶著嬰兒肥的IU其實也有點肉肉的，穿熱褲時更加明顯，完全不幹瘦，筆直的雙腿讓人真的很羡慕呢。 甚至有韓國網民稱IU才是「蜜大腿」的創世者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cfile10.uf.tistory.com/original/1126C7374DC58FA40967FA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile10.uf.tistory.com%2Foriginal%2F1126C7374DC58FA40967FA&h=333a71f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.onlifezone.com/files/attach/images/6006007/045/058/006/090725_000002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.onlifezone.com%2Ffiles%2Fattach%2Fimages%2F6006007%2F045%2F058%2F006%2F090725_000002.jpg&h=88e1b3f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.onlifezone.com/files/attach/images/6006007/045/058/006/090725_000013.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.onlifezone.com%2Ffiles%2Fattach%2Fimages%2F6006007%2F045%2F058%2F006%2F090725_000013.jpg&h=5330a72a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.onlifezone.com/files/attach/images/6006007/045/058/006/090725_000022.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.onlifezone.com%2Ffiles%2Fattach%2Fimages%2F6006007%2F045%2F058%2F006%2F090725_000022.jpg&h=a6179b71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.onlifezone.com/files/attach/images/6006007/045/058/006/090725_000030.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.onlifezone.com%2Ffiles%2Fattach%2Fimages%2F6006007%2F045%2F058%2F006%2F090725_000030.jpg&h=f349884f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過有資深網友糾正稱，「蜜大腿」一詞最早使用要追溯到天上智喜的Sunday，她才是真正的「創始人」，只是當時整團人氣並不高，才沒能讓「蜜大腿」火起來，直到碰上了AS時期的大勢U-IE~<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-09-30/120586-775573.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-09-30%2F120586-775573.png&h=0b54acf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-09-30/120586-775576.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-09-30%2F120586-775576.png&h=43b4a295&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0167c3fb943465e7e57d493fe9522b9dfd5212b","tid":1607330,"uid":34643,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:56:08.000Z","msg":"為各位data著想, 自己禁入去睇, 三思而後行<br />\n<a href=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/TLlr0n029kMveApYK9/source.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FTLlr0n029kMveApYK9%2Fsource.gif&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=873f617c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://media.giphy.com/media/TLlr0n029kMveApYK9/source.gif</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/l3mZiFd52biawiNJC/source.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fl3mZiFd52biawiNJC%2Fsource.gif&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk