07bae78988674cf52ab5d5c3df5566de","tid":1607330,"uid":7699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:04:50.000Z","msg":"唔係IU<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b081b5d152cfd1d1b1d8ef27852955e2fe7e1cd","tid":1607330,"uid":288786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:14:12.000Z","msg":"又跟民權抗爭老將的法國朋友聊天，當然論及香港的反送中運動，朋友說，看到香港警察一身造價不菲的裝備，頭部更用非常堅固的頭盔完全包裹，鐵甲人一樣，非常安全，但他說，非常奇怪，香港的抗爭者竟然不會向這些防暴警頭盔的保護鏡投擲任何顏料，個個防暴警的頭盔保護鏡竟然一塵不染。他說，投擲顏料相當容易，而保護鏡一旦看不清，就要把保護鏡拉起，甚至要卸下頭盔，自衛能力就大減，或要以真面目示人。"},{"pid":"dd2b9f2c3db3df80e3218106eb6ae05c06064ee2","tid":1607330,"uid":184570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:18:02.000Z","msg":"唔係IU都開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d88d79e93aa45efd898313f113b629b550bc6b","tid":1607330,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd2b9f2c3db3df80e3218106eb6ae05c06064ee2","tid":1607330,"uid":184570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:18:02.000Z","msg":"唔係IU都開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T22:17:57.000Z","msg":"文盲？"},{"pid":"2fcb483cac9a3a2effa9ff850bb88010ad87edea","tid":1607330,"uid":34643,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T00:36:30.000Z","msg":"皮光肉滑<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3o7btZOhVvLVab9mw0/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3o7btZOhVvLVab9mw0%2Fgiphy.gif&h=9facea64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cfile26.uf.tistory.com/original/275F1D4C560E5F7E04A6D5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile26.uf.tistory.com%2Foriginal%2F275F1D4C560E5F7E04A6D5&h=e9bc705b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/TWQiGb4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTWQiGb4.g